title: Large Top Floor Apartment, Remodeled Inside, Wood Floors, Fresh Paint
posting_body: ['Large Top Floor Apartment, Remodeled Inside, Wood Floors, Fresh Paint, Corner Unit!', 'Property Address', '3036 Huff Ave - 06 | San Jose, CA 95128', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Presidential Real Estate, Inc', 'Description', '3036 Huff Ave #6, San Jose, CA  95128  (Winchester/Magliocco)', 'The Birchwood Apartments is pleased to offer a large and spacious top floor apartment with 1 bedroom and 1 bathroom.', ' The home has been recently renovated to include a newer kitchen, bathroom, wood floors, fresh paint, new baseboards, and new appliances.', ' The kitchen includes wood cabinets with granite counters, stainless steel sink, electric stove/oven, and a fridge.', ' The bathroom has been updated to feaute a wood vanity with granite counters, tile floors, tile shower enclosure and glass shower doors.', 'The complex is located near Santana Row and Westfield Valley Fair with convenient access to shopping, dining, banks, and Starbucks.', 'The apartment includes water and garbage.', ' One year lease required.', ' No pets except for required service animals.', ' Onsite laundry facility.', 'Cal DRE# 01998337', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,995.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,800.00']
